data.description: Move right in to this beautiful home built in 2015 on 1.64 acres in Golden Gate Estates. SELLERS ARE OFFERING $5000 IN CLOSING COST ASSISTANCE  This lovely home has a double door entry leading to an elegant foyer. Large formal dining room, Great room, Spacious kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, breakfast bar and breakfast nook. 3 bedrooms plus den with french doors, 2 full bathrooms with granite countertops, 2 car Garage. Tray ceilings, crown molding, tile throughout the home, and laminate in bedrooms. Kinetico water filter. Concrete driveway with extra parking area. Screened in lanai. Conveniently located just minutes to the Orangetree Publix Plaza and the Big Corkscrew Regional Park. Completely cleared and fenced property with an entry gate, plenty of room for a guest house, pool and storage.   Come enjoy tranquility and nature on your own private estate.
